### VS Code REST Client - Dating App APIs
### Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code to use this file

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ========== MOBILE OTP LOGIN ==========

### Send Mobile OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/api/mobile/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobile": "9876543210",
  "country_code": "+1"
}

### Verify Mobile OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/api/mobile/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobile": "9876543210",
  "country_code": "+1",
  "otp": "1111",
  "device_id": "mobile-device-456",
  "device_type": "android",
  "model": "Samsung Galaxy S23"
}

